(56, 3, '6', 'CBD Choco', 'Choco CBD', 'Choco CBD', 'Choco CBD', 0, 534.71, 0, 512.5, 24, 'cbd-choco-cbd-logistics', 'choco-cbd-cbd-logistics', 'choco-cbd-cbd-logistics', 'choco-cbd-cbd-logistics', '<div id=\"product-description-short\" itemprop=\"description\"><p>Content: 200g/400g/600g/800g/1000g ..</p>\n<p>Extraction: made in Switzerland </p>\n<p>Values: CBD 32%, THC&nbsp;0.1-0.3% (suitable EU)</p></div>', '<div id=\"product-description-short\" itemprop=\"description\"><p>Inhalt: 200g/400g/600g/800g/1000g..</p> <p>Extraktion: made in Switzerland </p> <p>Werte: CBD 32%, THC 0,1-0,3% (EU-fähig)</p></div>', '<div id=\"product-description-short\" itemprop=\"description\"><p>Contenu: 200g / 400g / 600g / 800g / 1000g ..</p> <p>Extraction: fabriqué en Suisse </p> <p>Valeurs: CBD 32%, THC 0.1-0.3% (éligible UE)</p></div>', '<div id=\"product-description-short\" itemprop=\"description\"><p>Contenuto: 200g/400g/600g/800g/1000g ..</p>\n<p>Estrazione: made in Switzerland </p>\n<p>Valori: CBD 32%, THC&nbsp;0.1-0.3% (idoneo EU)</p></div>', '<div class=\"product-description\"><p>CBD Choco is produced through the extraction of high quality CBD hemp grown in Switzerland.</p>\n<p>CBD Choco compact extract dark brown color suitable for dabbing and vaporization or more classic use.</p>\n<p>Cbd&nbsp;Logistics is able to produce well-made CBD Choco with a degree of purity CBD 32%, THC&nbsp;0.1-0.3% (suitable EU).</p>\n<p>Natural terpenes give the product its uniqueness. Nothing to do with Isolate CBD of which the analyzed terpenes are often 3 or 4.</p>\n<p>Cbd Logistics CBD Choco contains 33 natural terpenes extracted from female inflorescences of high quality Cannabis Sativa L.</p>\n<p>Among the types of dry extraction that has always been appreciated by end users, CBD Choco has a strong appearance, a characteristic odor and a typical compact consistency.</p>\n<p>Specifications:</p>\n<p>Content: 200g/400g/600g/800g/1000g ..</p>\n<p>Extraction: made in Switzerland </p>\n<p>Values: CBD 32%, THC&nbsp;0.1-0.3% (suitable&nbsp;EU)</p>\n<p>Appearance: dark brown color</p>\n<p>Odor: intense especially at the moment of preparation after breaking the dough</p>\n<p>Consistency:&nbsp;compact extract, sticky</p>\n<p>Original CBD Choco. Beware of imitations.</p>\n<p>CBD extractions and in general the products marketed by&nbsp;Cbd Logistics undergo rigorous internal quality controls in compliance with the current federal legislation on the matter and in compliance with the prerequisites of IG Hanf Switzerland sector association.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.admin.ch/opc/de/classified-compilation/20101220/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Current Swiss legal basis on the subject</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bag.admin.ch/bag/en/home.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">UFSP checked</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ighanf.ch/en/memberdirectory/cbd-logistics-sagl/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Founding Member IG Hanf Switzerland</a></p></div>', '<div class=\"product-description\"><p>Choco CBD wird durch die Extraktion von hochwertigem CBD-Hanf hergestellt, der in der Schweiz angebaut wird.</p> <p>Kompakter Extrakt aus dunkelbrauner Farbe, geeignet zum Tupfen und Verdampfen oder für den klassischen Gebrauch.</p> <p>Cbd Logistics ist in der Lage, Choco CBD von ausgezeichneter Verarbeitung mit einem Reinheitsgrad CBD 32%, THC 0,1-0,3% (EU-berechtigt) herzustellen.</p> <p>Natürliche Terpene verleihen dem Produkt seine Einzigartigkeit. Nichts mit CBD-Isolaten zu tun, von denen die analysierten Terpene oft 3 oder 4 sind. Cbd Logistics Choco CBD enthält 33 natürliche Terpene, die aus hochwertigen weiblichen Hanf Sativa L. Blütenständen gewonnen werden.</p> <p>Unter den Arten der Trockenextraktion, die von Endverbrauchern schon immer geschätzt wurden, hat Choco CBD ein starkes Aussehen, den charakteristischen Geruch und die typische kompakte Konsistenz.</p> <p>Spezifisch:</p> <p>Inhalt: 200g/400g/600g/800g/1000g..</p> <p>Extraktion: made in Switzerland </p> <p>Werte: CBD 32%, THC 0,1-0,3% (EU-fähig)</p> <p>Aussehen: dunkelbraune Farbe</p> <p>Geruch: intensiv vor allem zum Zeitpunkt der Zubereitung nach dem Brechen des Teigs</p> <p>Konsistenz: kompakter, klebriger Extrakt</p> <p>Choco CBD original. Vorsicht vor Imitationen. </p> <p>CBD-Extraktionen und generell die von Cbd Logistics vermarkteten Produkte unterliegen strengen internen Qualitätskontrollen in Übereinstimmung mit der aktuellen Bundesgesetzgebung zum Thema und in Übereinstimmung mit den Voraussetzungen des Branchenverbandes IG Hanf Schweiz.</p> <p><a href=\"https://www.admin.ch/opc/de/classified-compilation/20101220/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Aktuelle Schweizer Rechtsgrundlage zu diesem Thema</a></p> <p><a href=\"https://www.bag.admin.ch/bag/it/home.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">BAG geprüft</a></p> <p><a href=\"https://ighanf.ch/it/memberdirectory/cbd-logistics-sagl/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Gründungsmitglied IG Hanf Schweiz</a></p></div>', '<div class=\"product-description\"><p>Choco CBD est produit par l’extraction de chanvre CBD de haute qualité cultivé en Suisse.</p> <p>Extrait compact de couleur brun foncé adapté au dabbing et à la vaporisation ou à une utilisation plus classique.</p> <p>Cbd Logistics est capable de produire du Choco CBD d’excellente finition avec un degré de pureté CBD 32%, THC 0.1-0.3% (éligible UE).</p> <p>Les terpènes naturels donnent au produit son caractère unique. Rien à voir avec les isolats de CBD dont les terpènes analysés sont souvent 3 ou 4. Cbd Logistics Choco CBD contient 33 terpènes naturels extraits d’inflorescences femelles de chanvre Sativa L. de haute qualité.</p> <p>Parmi les types d’extraction à sec qui ont toujours été appréciés par les consommateurs finaux, Choco CBD a une apparence forte, l’odeur caractéristique et la consistance compacte typique.</p> <p>Spécifique:</p> <p>Contenu: 200g / 400g / 600g / 800g / 1000g ..</p> <p>Extraction: fabriqué en Suisse </p> <p>Valeurs: CBD 32%, THC 0.1-0.3% (éligible UE)</p> <p>Apparence: couleur brun foncé</p> <p>Odeur: intense surtout au moment de la préparation après la rupture de la pâte</p> <p>Consistance : extrait compact et collant</p> <p>Choco CBD original. Méfiez-vous des imitations. </p> <p>Les extractions de CBD et, en général, les produits commercialisés par Cbd Logistics sont soumis à des contrôles de qualité internes stricts conformément à la législation fédérale en vigueur en la matière et aux conditions préalables de l’association industrielle IG Hanf Suisse.</p> <p><a href=\"https://www.admin.ch/opc/de/classified-compilation/20101220/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Base juridique suisse actuelle en la matière</a></p> <p><a href=\"https://www.bag.admin.ch/bag/it/home.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Contrôle de l’OFSP</a></p> <p><a href=\"https://ighanf.ch/it/memberdirectory/cbd-logistics-sagl/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Membre fondateur IG Hanf Suisse</a></p></div>', '<div class=\"product-description\"><p>Choco CBD viene prodotto attraverso l\'estrazione di Canapa CBD di alta qualità coltivata in Svizzera.</p>\n<p>Estratto di natura compatta di colore&nbsp;marrone scuro&nbsp;adatto al dabbing e la vaporizzazione o all\'utilizzo più classico.</p>\n<p>Cbd&nbsp;Logistics è in grado di produrre Choco CBD&nbsp;di ottima fattura con grado di purezza CBD 32%, THC&nbsp;0.1-0.3% (idoneo EU).</p>\n<p>I terpeni naturali donano al prodotto la sua unicità. Nulla a che vedere con Isolate CBD di cui i terpeni analizzati risultano spesso 3 o 4. Cbd Logistics Choco CBD&nbsp;contiene 33 terpeni naturali estratti da inflorescenze femminili di Canapa Sativa L. di alta qualità.</p>\n<p>Tra le tipologie di&nbsp;estrazione secca da sempre apprezzato dai consumatori finali Choco CBD ha un aspetto deciso, l’odore caratteristico e la consistenza compatta tipica.</p>\n<p>Specifiche:</p>\n<p>Contenuto: 200g/400g/600g/800g/1000g ..</p>\n<p>Estrazione: made in Switzerland </p>\n<p>Valori: CBD 32%, THC&nbsp;0.1-0.3%&nbsp;(idoneo EU)</p>\n<p>Aspetto: colore&nbsp;marrone scuro</p>\n<p>Odore: intenso soprattutto nel momento della preparazione dopo aver spezzato il panetto</p>\n<p>Consistenza: estratto di natura compatta, appiccicoso</p>\n<p>Choco CBD originale. Attenzione alle imitazioni.  </p>\n<p>Le estrazioni CBD ed in generale i prodotti commercializzati da&nbsp;Cbd Logistics subiscono rigorosi controlli di qualità interni nel rispetto dell’attuale normativa federale in materia e nel rispetto dei prerequisiti di IG Hanf Switzerland associazione di settore.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.admin.ch/opc/de/classified-compilation/20101220/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Attuale base legale Svizzera in materia</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bag.admin.ch/bag/it/home.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">UFSP checked</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ighanf.ch/it/memberdirectory/cbd-logistics-sagl/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Membro fondatore IG Hanf Switzerland</a></p></div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3-3-1.1', 1, 0, NULL, NULL);
